## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Escopo de Negocio (Regra #5){{else}}Business Scope (Rule #5){{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
**PERMITIDO**: layout, UX, navegacao nativa, captura de fotos/GPS/sensores, push notifications, armazenamento local, chamadas API.

**PROIBIDO**: calculos de dominio, regras de negocio, logica de sincronizacao complexa (pertence ao backend).
{{else}}
**ALLOWED**: layout, UX, native navigation, photo/GPS/sensor capture, push notifications, local storage, API calls.

**FORBIDDEN**: domain calculations, business rules, complex sync logic (belongs to backend).
{{/if}}

